      <title>南非联合政府股价上涨刺激财富增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-africa-household-wealth-rises-to-highest-level-in-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非央行表示，第二季度南非家庭财富增加，因为其资产市值的增幅超过了负债的增幅，部分原因是股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-africa-household-wealth-rises-to-highest-level-in-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴斯夫大幅削减股息，考虑将子公司上市，因业绩下滑加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/basf-seeks-overhaul-with-lower-dividend-focus-on-core-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为广泛改革的一部分，巴斯夫欧洲公司将削减股息并剥离资产，改革可能涉及关闭更多德国工厂，以应对高昂的能源价格和中国市场的持续低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/basf-seeks-overhaul-with-lower-dividend-focus-on-core-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
